Package org.openbel.framework.tools

Contains BEL tools.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
Backtrack The Backtrack BEL command-line application.
BelCheck BelCheck is a CommandLineApplication to validate the syntax and semantics of a BEL or XBEL document.
CacheManager CacheManager is a CommandLineApplication to manage the BELFramework cache and provides the following functionality: List the contents of the cache. Load a resource file into the cache. Load resources from a resource index file into the cache. Update all resources in the cache. Purge all resources in the cache. Generates a hash for a local file.
